product_name: Yakima SkyBox Cargo Box Cargo Net
long_description: Keep your gear protected and in place in your Yakima(TM) Skybox or other cargo box with this cargo net. Uses 8 plastic attachment hooks to affix directly into the Skybox series' integrated track system to secure your gear. Unstretched net is 32 inches by 20 inches and is divided into 4x4 squares.
short_description: Keep your gear protected and in place in your Yakima(TM) Skybox or other cargo box with this cargo net.
